# Command Files Guide

The [`src/command/`](mdc:src/command) directory contains command implementations for the extension:

- [`createAmpersandExpression.ts`](mdc:src/command/createAmpersandExpression.ts): Creates an ampersand expression node.
- [`createConditionalExpression.ts`](mdc:src/command/createConditionalExpression.ts): Creates a conditional expression node.
- [`createForwardCommand.ts`](mdc:src/command/createForwardCommand.ts): Creates a forward command node.
- [`remove.ts`](mdc:src/command/remove.ts): Removes a node from the AST.
- [`removeChildren.ts`](mdc:src/command/removeChildren.ts): Removes all children from a node.
- [`showMachineId.ts`](mdc:src/command/showMachineId.ts): Shows the machine ID.
- [`swapWithNextSibling.ts`](mdc:src/command/swapWithNextSibling.ts): Swaps a node with its next sibling.
- [`wrapWithDiv.ts`](mdc:src/command/wrapWithDiv.ts): Wraps a node with a div element.
